#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools/gnu/pkgconfigdeps.rst:91
msgid "Components"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools/gnu/pkgconfigdeps.rst:93
msgid ""
"If a recipe uses :ref:`components<package_information_components>`, the "
"files generated will be *<[PKG-NAME]-[COMP-NAME]>.pc* with their "
"corresponding flags and require relations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools/gnu/pkgconfigdeps.rst:96
msgid ""
"Additionally, a *<PKG-NAME>.pc* is generated to maintain compatibility for "
"consumers with recipes that start supporting components. This *<PKG-NAME>."
"pc* file will declare all the components of the package as requires while "
"the rest of the fields will be empty, relying on the propagation of flags "
"coming from the components *<[PKG-NAME]-[COMP-NAME]>.pc* files."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools/gnu/pkgconfigdeps.rst:104
msgid "Properties"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools/gnu/pkgconfigdeps.rst:106
msgid "The following properties affect the ``PkgConfigDeps`` generator:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools/gnu/pkgconfigdeps.rst:108
msgid ""
"**pkg_config_name** property will define the name of the generated ``*.pc`` "
"file (``xxxxx.pc``)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools/gnu/pkgconfigdeps.rst:109
msgid ""
"**pkg_config_aliases** property sets some aliases of any package/component "
"name for *pkg_config* generator. This property only accepts list-like Python "
"objects."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools/gnu/pkgconfigdeps.rst:110
msgid ""
"**pkg_config_custom_content** property will add user defined content to the "
"*.pc* files created by this generator."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools/gnu/pkgconfigdeps.rst:111
msgid ""
"**component_version** property sets a custom version to be used in the "
"``Version`` field belonging to the created ``*.pc`` file for that component."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools/gnu/pkgconfigdeps.rst:113
msgid ""
"These properties can be defined at global ``cpp_info`` level or at component "
"level."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools/gnu/pkgconfigdeps.rst:115
msgid "Example:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools/gnu/pkgconfigdeps.rst:117
msgid ""
"def package_info(self):\n"
"    custom_content = \"datadir=${prefix}/share\"\n"
"    self.cpp_info.set_property(\"pkg_config_custom_content\", "
"custom_content)\n"
"    self.cpp_info.set_property(\"pkg_config_name\", \"myname\")\n"
"    self.cpp_info.components[\"mycomponent\"]."
"set_property(\"pkg_config_name\", \"componentname\")\n"
"    self.cpp_info.components[\"mycomponent\"]."
"set_property(\"pkg_config_aliases\", [\"alias1\", \"alias2\"])\n"
"    self.cpp_info.components[\"mycomponent\"]."
"set_property(\"component_version\", \"1.14.12\")"
msgstr ""

